<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Furrow1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Furrow,</orth> subst. a trench in the earth made by the plough: <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.135" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 135</bibl>. Hence a hollow made by wrinkles in the face: <bibl n="shak. son 22.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 22, 3</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>